  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to assess the effect of CICATRIX (Asian Gotu Kola or Pennywort)
      usage in the treatment of epidermic burns or post surgical scars. The duration of this phase
      2 clinical trial will be two months.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
