  <intervention>
    <intervention_type>Other</intervention_type>
    <intervention_name>Cicatrix cream</intervention_name>
    <description>We will be carried out the topical application of the product (Cicatrix cream) in the epidermic burns or post surgical scars by administration fo the patients twice a day during two months to a dose of 0,1 ml of cream for each cm of surface, being controlled by the specialist in biweekly consultations.
To the patient will be explained the technique of the application.</description>
